OL,3,CQueen records special broadcast with
OL,4,CJohn and Amy Hunt after family's murder
OL,6,FThe Queen has recorded a radio
OL,7,Fbroadcast with BBC racing commentator
OL,8,FJohn Hunt and his daughter Amy, whose
OL,9,Ffamily were murdered at their home.
OL,11,FLouise Hunt, 25, her sister Hannah
OL,12,FHunt, 28, and their mother Carol Hunt,
OL,13,F61, were killed by Kyle Clifford, 27 `
OL,14,FLouise's ex-partner ` in a quiet cul-
OL,15,Fde-sac in Bushey, Hertfordshire, on
OL,16,FJuly 9 last year.
