OL,3,CQueen records special broadcast with
OL,4,CJohn and Amy Hunt after family's murder
OL,6,FThe announcement of the special
OL,7,Fbroadcast, set to air on New Year's
OL,8,FEve, coincides with the final day of
OL,9,Fthe United Nations' 16 Days of
OL,10,FActivism Against Gender-Based Violence.
OL,12,FCamilla welcomed Mr Hunt and Amy to
OL,13,Fthe Garden Room at Clarence House last
OL,14,Fmonth for a discussion that also
OL,15,Fincluded former prime minister
OL,16,FBaroness Theresa May and was chaired
OL,17,Fby BBC broadcaster Emma Barnett.
