OL,3,CQueen records special broadcast with
OL,4,CJohn and Amy Hunt after family's murder
OL,6,FThe conversation will be aired in a
OL,7,Fspecial edition of BBC Radio 4's Today
OL,8,Fprogramme, guest-edited by Baroness
OL,9,FMay.
OL,11,FAhead of the broadcast, a fundraising
OL,12,Fgala will be held on Thursday night to
OL,13,Flaunch The Hunt Family Fund.
OL,15,FMr Hunt and Amy set up the fund in
OL,16,Fmemory of Carol, Louise and Hannah to
OL,17,Fraise money for charities and causes
OL,18,Fthat support and inspire young women.
