OL,6,FThe racing commentator told BBC News:
OL,7,F"From the moment I wake up, I say good
OL,8,Fmorning to each of them.
OL,10,F"Sometimes I say out loud to Hannah
OL,11,Fand Louise, 'Girls, sorry I can't be
OL,12,Fwith you, I'm with your mum at the
OL,13,Fmoment'. As I close my eyes at night,
OL,14,FI chat to them as well. So yeah, very
OL,15,Fclose (to me) all the time."
OL,17,FAmy said: "My mum, Hannah and Louise
OL,18,Fbecame a statistic. They became
OL,19,Fvictims of Kyle Clifford.
